sequenceDiagram
    participant WF as Workflow Code
    participant HOST as Runtime Host
    participant CD as controld
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant SLACK as Slack (optional)
    participant HUMAN as Human

    WF->>HOST: sdk.interrupt(payload)
    HOST->>CD: IPC: Interrupt message
    CD->>DB: Create WorkflowInterrupt<br/>(status=Pending)
    CD->>DB: Update WorkflowRun<br/>(status=Interrupted)

    opt Slack notification
        CD->>SLACK: Post message with action buttons
    end

    Note over HOST: Workflow process pauses<br/>(awaiting stdin resume message)

    alt Via API
        HUMAN->>CD: POST /interrupts/:id/resume<br/>{ response }
    else Via Slack
        HUMAN->>SLACK: Click approve/reject button
        SLACK->>CD: POST /webhook/slack/interactions
    end

    CD->>DB: Update WorkflowInterrupt<br/>(status=Resumed, response)
    CD->>HOST: IPC: ResumeInterrupt message
    HOST->>WF: Return response to sdk.interrupt()
    Note over WF: Workflow continues execution
